        <mxCell id="pGn-SHoEVF3mf9oFJCtO-24" value="DNS queries from the Internet reach the appliance through Firewall-1, and the appliance sends its replies back through Firewall-1.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;DNS queries from the internal network reach the appliance through Firewall-2, but because there is only one default route, the appliance erroneously sends DNS replies to the DMZ interface on Firewall-1." style="text;strokeColor=none;align=left;fillColor=none;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
